---
import Layout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Athena AI | Live Demo">
  <main class="demo-container">
    
    <header class="demo-header">
      <span class="badge">LIVE DEMO</span>
      <h1>Athena<span class="accent">AI</span></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Voice-Activated Study Companion • Powered by Llama 3.2 & Python</p>
    </header>

    <div class="video-wrapper">
      <video controls poster="/images/poster-image.jpg" class="main-video">
        <source src="/athena-demo.mov" type="video/quicktime">
        <source src="/athena-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
      </video>
      
      <div class="tech-stack">
        <span class="tech-tag">Python / Flask</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">WebSockets</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">Llama 3.2</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">EdgeTTS</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="notice-box">
      <span class="notice-icon">⚠️</span>
      <div class="notice-content">
        <strong>Heads up:</strong> This video shows the app running on my local machine. 
        Because this project uses a custom Python backend (Flask) to handle the 
        real-time voice processing, you need to have the server running locally to use it live. Hosting a real-time LLM with voice processing requires dedicated cloud GPUs, which are outside my current budget.
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="project-details">
      <div class="detail-card">
        <h3>How I Built It</h3>
        <p>I didn't want a standard chatbot, so I engineered a custom backend using <strong>Python and Flask</strong>. The hardest part was getting the audio to feel "real-time," so I used WebSockets to stream data instantly between the AI and the browser without lag.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card">
        <h3>Why It Matters</h3>
        <p>Most AI study tools feel robotic. I designed Athena to use the <strong>Feynman Technique</strong>—meaning she actually pushes back if I'm wrong. My goal wasn't just to write code, but to design a personality that makes studying feel less lonely.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Return to Main Page</a>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Local Styles for Demo Page */
  .demo-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Header */
  .badge {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
    color: var(--accent-color);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 99px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .accent { color: var(--accent-color); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #888; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  /* Video Player */
  .video-wrapper {
    background: #000;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .main-video { width: 100%; display: block; aspect-ratio: 16/9; }

  .tech-stack {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .tech-tag { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #aaa; font-family: monospace; }

  /* Python Notice Box */
  .notice-box {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .notice-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .notice-content { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.5; }
  .notice-content strong { color: #fff; }

  /* Details Grid */
  .project-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .detail-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .detail-card h3 { color: var(--accent-color); margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .detail-card p { color: #bbb; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

  .back-link {
    color: #666;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--accent-color); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-details { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }
</style>